Package classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Customer
    Represents a customer who is at the restaurant
    Invoice
    Represents the Invoice of an Order
    MenuItem
    Represents individual (Food) Menu Item
    A MenuItem is a SaleItem, with MenuType
    Order
    Represents the order at the restaurant
    Person
    Represents a person who is at the restaurant A person can be a customer or a staff of the restaurant
    Reservation
    Represents the reservation at the restaurant
    Restaurant
    The Restaurant class will provide a static database for the application.
    SaleItem
    Abstract class, represents an item that the Restaurant is selling.
    Set
    Represents a (Food Menu) Set
    A Set is a SaleItem, that is made up of 1 or more MenuItem.
    Staff
    Represents a customer who works at the restaurant
    Table
    Represents a table in the restaurant The table can be occupied or vacated
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    MenuItem.MenuType
    Represent type of (Food) Menu Item
    Can be a Main Dish, Side Dish, Drink, Dessert etc
    Person.Gender
    Enumeration type used to determine the gender of the person
    Table.Status
    Enumeration type used to determine the status of the table
